{
  "page": "Bone flute",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>bone flute</b> is a musical instrument of the woodwind family. It is a type of <a href=\"/index.php/Flute\" title=\"Flute\">flute</a> made of <a href=\"/index.php/Bone\" title=\"Bone\">bone</a>, like <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/paleolithic_flutes\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:paleolithic flutes\">paleolithic flutes</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_events\">Recent events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bone_flute&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bone_flute&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>One of <a href=\"/index.php/Yurkhaz_zo_Yunzak\" title=\"Yurkhaz zo Yunzak\">Yurkhaz zo Yunzak</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slaves</a> plays a bone flute whilst the <a href=\"/index.php/Goat_boy\" title=\"Goat boy\">goat boy</a> dances a grotesque jig at <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a>'s banquet for Yurkhaz.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bone_flut